txt.en: Damrod can be found in Barad Orhant in Minas Morgul.\n\nYou should talk to Damrod.
Wights can be found in the Circle of Sorrow in Minas Morgul.\n\nYou should defeat any wights that you find.
'You have done the Rangers of Ithilien a great service. I thank you for your efforts assisting us upon the Circle of Sorrow. We shall retake the Dead City soon enough!'
'We must lessen the numbers of the Dead who walk upon the Circle of Sorrow. I ask you to defeat any wights that you find as you venture out into the city.'
Damrod wishes to defeat the many wights that stalk the Circle of Sorrow in Minas Morgul.
Defeat deadly sorrow-wights in Minas Morgul ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
